OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FOvernight rain should soon clear on
OL,7,FThursday to leave plenty of sunshine
OL,8,Ffor the afternoon. Largely dry and
OL,9,Fsettled thereafter too, and starting
OL,10,Fto feel warmer again in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
